@startuml approach3-linq-abbreviated
title **Approach 3: CosmosClient + FakeCosmosHandler — LINQ Query Flow (Abbreviated)**

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

actor "Test Code" as Test
participant "CosmosClient\n(real SDK)" as SDK
participant "Container\n(real SDK)" as SDKContainer
participant "CosmosLinqQuery-\nProvider (SDK)" as LinqProvider
participant "IOrderedQueryable<T>" as Queryable
participant "HttpClient" as Http
participant "FakeCosmosHandler" as Handler
participant "CosmosSqlParser" as Parser
participant "InMemoryContainer" as IMC
participant "QueryResultCache" as Cache
participant "SDK FeedIterator<T>" as SDKIter

== Setup ==
Test -> IMC ** : new InMemoryContainer(…)
Test -> Handler ** : new FakeCosmosHandler(container)
Test -> SDK ** : new CosmosClient(…, HttpClientFactory)

== Get Container ==
Test -> SDK ++ : client.GetContainer(databaseId, containerId)
SDK --> Test -- : Container (real SDK proxy)

== LINQ Expression Building ==
Test -> SDKContainer ++ : container.GetItemLinqQueryable<T>()
SDKContainer -> LinqProvider ** : CosmosLinqQueryProvider
SDKContainer -> Queryable ** : IOrderedQueryable<T>
SDKContainer --> Test -- : IOrderedQueryable<T>

Test -> Queryable : .Where() / .OrderBy() / .Select()\n(builds Expression Tree)

== LINQ-to-SQL Translation ==
Test -> Queryable ++ : .ToFeedIterator()
Queryable -> LinqProvider : Translate expression tree → SQL
LinqProvider --> Queryable : Cosmos SQL + parameters
Queryable --> Test -- : FeedIterator<T>

== Query Plan + Execution (same as Approach 3 SQL) ==
loop while HasMoreResults
  Test -> SDKIter ++ : ReadNextAsync()
  SDKIter -> Http : POST (query plan, then query)
  Http -> Handler : SendAsync → HandleQueryPlanAsync()\nthen HandleQueryAsync()
  Handler -> Parser : TryParse() + SimplifySdkQuery()
  Handler -> IMC : GetItemQueryIterator → FilterItemsByQuery()
  Handler -> Handler : DrainIterator() → BuildPagedResponse()
  Handler -> Cache : cache results
  Handler --> Http : 200 OK + paginated JSON
  Http --> SDKIter : response → SDK pipeline merges
  SDKIter --> Test -- : FeedResponse<T>
end

note over Test
  Key: LINQ → SQL by real SDK,
  then SQL executed through CosmosSqlParser
  (tests full LINQ-to-SQL translation)
end note

@enduml
